      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "from scipy.integrate import *\n",
        "from numpy.fft import *\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "336b758e-a003-4094-86fa-15e2e5bca1dd",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "336b758e-a003-4094-86fa-15e2e5bca1dd"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def func(X,t):\n",
        "    N=int(len(X)/2)\n",
        "    k=1\n",
        "    m=1\n",
        "\n",
        "    #A bemenetként kapott array fele a kitérések, fele a sebességek:\n",
        "    x=np.array(X[:N])\n",
        "    v=np.array(X[N:2*N])\n",
        "\n",
        "    D = (k/m) * ( np.diag([-2]*N) + np.diag([1]*(N-1),1) + np.diag([1]*(N-1),-1) )\n",
        "\n",
        "    a = D@x\n",
        "\n",
        "    U=np.zeros(2*N)\n",
        "\n",
        "    for i in range(N):\n",
        "        #A kimenet is olyan formában legyen, mint a bemenet:\n",
        "        U[i]=v[i]\n",
        "        U[N+i]=a[i]\n",
        "\n",
        "    return(U)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "09361764-0643-4e12-add5-93b65b63c920",
      "metadata": {

      },

      "source": [
        "n=100 #golyók száma"

    },

      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "X0=np.array([0 for i in range(2*n)])\n",
        "X0[n]=1\n",
        "#Kezdeti feltételek."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "94724554-64fa-4218-a17a-6a5466bed7d7",

      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "t1=200\n",

        "t=np.linspace(0,t1,N)"
      ]

      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "u=odeint(func,X0,t)\n",
        "#diffegy megoldása"
      ]
